Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 笑起来多像你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 像亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字叫吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真忍心扔下这可爱的孩子去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后一次任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会有这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这样善良的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不该上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想让他们生活在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 现在必须战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时光飞逝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是勇气纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是漫长战争开始的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会见到父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天国的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争还没有结束
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屈身于红色星球的战士们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们理想乡的实现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的计划即将 进入最终篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘扬在地球神圣大地的日子不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广场上的机动战士展快要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到个绝佳的景点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去就上车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勒布鲁斯 考出驾照了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这车是问爸爸借的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 有个派对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好像是吉欧爷爷的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧最亲爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪里有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨环基地防线内发现未知物体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综合解析系统认为90%是维甘移动要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有发现这庞然大物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士部队紧急出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时命令周边舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在敌方移动要塞上 发现巨大热量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是高功率光束武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见了吗 德勒尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始的钟声 响起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉 是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 你父亲的遗物？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基没听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧父亲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸是联邦军机师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我出生后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一次调查漂流船的任务时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 别瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后 军队前往调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了这块AGE装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 地球上也要打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人… 那就是维甘…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急召回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知不当班的士官 会还他们假期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告机动战士队情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布兰克斯第7小队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿比斯小队也即将出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 什么勇气纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 这就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿比斯队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜路亚 乔纳森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥迪克　德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部不会把坏情况告诉前线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是听见了吧 皮特的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮特… 那个通讯员？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次听到皮特那种发颤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他外遇被老婆发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可见情况之危急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 战场福尔摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之这次不同往常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克兰修特装型 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名为伊泽尔坎特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活在火星圈的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独立国家维甘的代表者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 地球种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘在此宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式开始侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵略地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各军区报告出现维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅限于奥利巴诺兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直隐藏在地球上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民们请迅速前往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿伦特河的避难区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复 居民们请迅速前往阿伦特河…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车 勒布鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再耽搁我们自身难保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我在这里下车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂 你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说我没劝过你们
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着三个孩子打算这么过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去喊军人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕 一起过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去避难区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去避难区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们被落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用您的车送他们走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平民去阿伦特河避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没接到通知吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军对平民孩子见死不救？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上士 事态紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂 孩子拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事？ 不上车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也和吉欧一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你照顾好这些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷的高达是最强的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我们去哪儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去启动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 救世主登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天该告诉我藏高达的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用力拉操纵杆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是核心战机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核心战机 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候混进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利巴诺兹被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让歌姬号做好出发准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管那么多 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号是爷爷以前搭乘的战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然是艘老旧船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要有那艘船和高达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利巴诺兹就有救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达在那上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接驾驶核心战机靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西的驾驶就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人驾驶不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G拦截机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会变形成高达是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是变形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是合体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合体？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意听着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达是由G拦截机和核心战机合体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组成一台机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上开始合体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是还在飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 电脑会负责细节操作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…这也太突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 把AGE装置插入右手插口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后打开30号到35号开关
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据屏幕指示拉动拉杆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后按下操纵杆上的G键
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达AGE-3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别松懈 好戏才刚开场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吗 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 驱动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 继承高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来 驱动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了 可是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达的操纵方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你玩的模拟战一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是普通的游戏机？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷为了这一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光束军刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放跑它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是用歌姬号光子爆破炮技术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研发的新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西格玛希斯步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮击型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏里打过
